&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.linkedin.com/in/gustavo-dos-rem%c3%a9dios-da-silva-paula-995a04181&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Gustavo do Remédios da Silva Paula&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
